title.narrative: % of primary health care facilities managing cold chain system according to national standards

actual.value: 2018:61% of primary health care facilities nationally are equipped by standard refrigerators based on WHO standard requirements. This result was achieved due to advocacy of UNICEF to allocate funds from SWAP budget to procure refrigerators.
